Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}とめられない You can’t kill my vibe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.68,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}自由に I can blow your mind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}何度だって You’ll see me rise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:03.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Tryna get to me and pay the price
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}描いた未来へ　進んで行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Won’t look back
