Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.37,0:02:26.54,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Attitude
Dialogue: 1,0:01:06.34,0:01:10.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}走自己的路 莫要阻拦
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.05,0:01:12.64,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}迈向巅峰
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.01,0:01:15.56,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}昂首挺胸 因为我知道
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.56,0:01:16.51,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}为我骄傲的人生
Dialogue: 1,0:01:16.51,0:01:18.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别跟我谈规矩
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.06,0:01:22.27,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}让我住手？ 想限制我就是徒劳
Dialogue: 1,0:01:22.27,0:01:26.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}震耳欲聋 此刻扳机声响起
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.74,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}小子 你很张狂
Dialogue: 1,0:01:28.74,0:01:30.36,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}感觉不会输
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.45,0:01:35.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}别停 装填决心的子弹
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.78,0:01:40.87,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}瞄准目标 莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.29,0:01:48.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.34,0:01:52.18,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.18,0:01:54.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.51,0:01:59.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}不可阻挡 不受干扰气势
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.39,0:02:00.68,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}随手颠覆你的想象
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}周而复始 浴火重生
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.52,0:02:03.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}招惹我会付出代价
Dialogue: 1,0:02:03.98,0:02:07.02,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}向描绘的未来前行而已
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.02,0:02:09.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}莫回头
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.78,0:02:15.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}请看我的态度
Dialogue: 1,0:02:15.07,0:02:18.20,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}毫不犹豫的心情
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.04,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}若不相信 我将证明
Dialogue: 1,0:02:21.04,0:02:23.79,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}那就请看我的态度
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.28,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Kill shot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.62,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Kill shot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.96,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Kill shot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.92,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Kill shot
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.59,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Pull the, pull the trigger
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.71,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Ah, まとまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.67,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}待って、まとまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.38,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}当たり前じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.38,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}それ、当たり前じゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.05,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}明日から中学生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}頭ん中パンクしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.76,0:21:24.76,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}No, it cannot be true
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.22,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}バグった将来のビジョン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Oh no, oh no, oh no
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.39,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}明日から Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.44,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}Ride, ride or die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}提出コンテンツ　要チェック
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}Tick tock tick tock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.77,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}前　前ならえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.19,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}Yah　ついていくしかないじゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.07,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}グルチャのテンポ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.07,0:21:37.65,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}欠けていた情熱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.65,0:21:39.36,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}上がってくモチベ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.61,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Don’t stop, pop, pop
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.82,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}We’re going up, up, up higher
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.08,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}暗闇の中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:46.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}無音で drive
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.58,0:21:49.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}孤独な傷跡が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.58,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}名前を呼ぶ声に今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.09,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}満たされ癒えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.13,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}始まったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.34,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}駆け出す未来は今
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.22,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}狙い定めた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.22,0:22:01.63,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}Because I’m a winner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:05.01,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}迷うたびに笑い飛ばしていけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.93,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}外さない弾道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.43,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}Because I’m a winner
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.23,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}この弾丸は fire fire
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.23,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur1\fscx60\fscy60\pos(916,0)}たま
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.69,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}Breaking the chains
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:15.15,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}夢はもうNever ever　捨てない promise
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.11,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}I will never give up, give up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.61,0:22:18.98,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Give up, give up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.07,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}I’m on a rampage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.78,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}Here comes my kill shot
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.62,0:21:04.28,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}致命一击
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.04,0:21:07.62,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}致命一击
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.41,0:21:10.96,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}致命一击
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.71,0:21:13.92,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}致命一击
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.59,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}扣下 扣下扳机
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.71,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}啊 手忙脚乱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.71,0:21:17.67,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}根本 理不清头绪
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.67,0:21:18.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}当然的事
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.38,0:21:19.38,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}当然 理所当然
Dialogue: 1,0:21:19.38,0:21:21.05,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}明天开始上中学
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.05,0:21:22.76,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}脑袋要爆炸了
