Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.77,0:21:29.39,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}明天开始重启
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.39,0:21:30.44,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}过命交情
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.44,0:21:31.52,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}提出的内容请务必确认
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.52,0:21:32.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}闹钟嘀嘀嗒嗒
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.69,0:21:33.77,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}向前 向前看齐
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.19,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}只能硬着头皮上
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.19,0:21:36.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}跟着群聊的节奏
