Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.82,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}我们要去往更高处
Dialogue: 1,0:21:42.82,0:21:45.08,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}黑暗之中
