Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.58,0:21:52.58,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}如今呼唤我的声音
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.58,0:21:55.09,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}痊愈我的伤痛
Dialogue: 1,0:21:55.09,0:21:56.13,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}要开始了
Dialogue: 1,0:21:56.13,0:21:58.34,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}此刻奔向未来
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.34,0:22:00.22,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}锁定目标
Dialogue: 1,0:22:00.22,0:22:01.63,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}只因我才是赢家
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.63,0:22:05.01,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}让迷茫一笑而过吧
Dialogue: 1,0:22:05.01,0:22:06.93,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}不偏移的弹道
Dialogue: 1,0:22:06.93,0:22:08.43,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}只因我才是赢家
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.43,0:22:10.23,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}这颗出膛的子弹
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.23,0:22:11.69,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}冲破枷锁
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.69,0:22:15.15,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax-0.1\blur2}坚定梦想 不弃承诺
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.15,0:22:17.11,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}永不放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:17.61,0:22:18.98,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}不放弃 不放弃
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.40,0:22:21.07,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}我已势不可当
Dialogue: 1,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.78,OP_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.1\blur2}这是我的致命一击
